      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I'M SWEET (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at Maitland following on from a second place finish (35.65) at Gosford the start prior. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Should bounce back. MIGHTY HENRY (6) crossed over from out wide but caught the leaders turning before drawing clear to score (22.62) at Maitland in a Grade 5 over 400m. Won at his only start from this draw. Expecting another bold showing. TURN UP ACE (3) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on his swift win the start prior, getting around The Gardens over 515m in 29.72. Should be in this for a long way. ZIPPING RUFFIAN (2) is a last-start close-up placegetter - solid claims again.",
